# Solo template references no env vars by default.
#
# When you add an interface (e.g. Telegram), declare its env vars here
# with placeholder values. Anything ending in `_env` in YAML is looked
# up from this file at startup.
#
# Example:
#   TEAMCTL_TELEGRAM_TOKEN=123456:AAH-...
#   TEAMCTL_TELEGRAM_CHATS=12345678
